modName: Re-colour Dark Brotherhood Male Armour Replacer
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple re-colour of the male set of Dark Brotherhood Armour

*This only edits the MALE set of armour
*This is a REPLACER not standalone

This simply bleeds the red into an ash type shading on the red parts of the armour.
author: Olaffsen
